 "cells": [
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "source": [
    "# 🔍 Spark Query Performance Analyzer\n",
    "\n",
    "Drop your SQL into a cell prefixed with `%analyze` and get instant bottleneck diagnostics.\n",
    "\n",
    "**Supported detections:**\n",
    "- Broadcast join misses\n",
    "- Full table scans\n",
    "- Cartesian products\n",
    "- Predicate pushdown failures\n",
    "- Repeated table scans\n",
    "- Shuffle size warnings\n",
    "- Skew indicators\n",
    "\n",
    "**Usage:**\n",
    "```python\n",
    "%analyze\n",
    "SELECT ... FROM ... WHERE ...\n",
    "```\n",
    "\n",
    "---"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "source": [
    "# Install the magic command — run this once per session\n",
    "import sys\n",
    "sys.path.insert(0, \"/tmp/spark_query_analyzer\")\n",
    "\n",
    "from spark_query_analyzer import register_analyze_magic\n",
    "register_analyze_magic()\n",
    "\n",
    "print(\"✅ %analyze magic registered. Use `%analyze` in any cell to start.\")"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "source": [
    "---"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "source": [
    "# Quick demo — paste any query below and run with %analyze\n",
    "%analyze\n",
    "SELECT \n",
    "    c.customer_id,\n",
    "    c.customer_name,\n",
    "    SUM(s.sale_amount) AS total_sales,\n",
    "    COUNT(DISTINCT p.product_id) AS product_count\n",
    "FROM fact_sales s\n",
    "JOIN dim_customer c ON s.customer_id = c.customer_id\n",
    "JOIN dim_product p ON s.product_id = p.product_id\n",
    "WHERE s.sale_date >= '2024-01-01'\n",
    "GROUP BY c.customer_id, c.customer_name\n",
    "HAVING SUM(s.sale_amount) > 10000\n",
    "ORDER BY total_sales DESC\n",
    "LIMIT 100"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "source": [
    "---"
   ]
  },
  {
